Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915: Eliminate obj->state usage from pre/post plane update
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f9a8c149e91ca18adfbadea5d562bc21197caf1a
Patch-mainline: v4.15-rc1
References: FATE#322643 bsc#1055900

Dig up the appropriate new crtc and plane states from the top level
atomic state in intel_pre_plane_update() and intel_post_plane_update().

Reviewed-by: Maarten Lankhorst <maarten.lankhorst@linux.intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Ville Syrjälä <ville.syrjala@linux.intel.com>
